commentAnnotations.text: Substantive new information appears in italics.
This amendment represents cumulative changes to the original protocol.
The diagnosis of macular edema due to RVO must be confirmed by the CRC.
Study treatment visits cannot occur earlier than 21 days after the previous study treatment visit.
Missed study treatments will not be made up.

studyDefinitionDocumentVersions.description: Protocol Amendment 2: Rationale includes increasing patient sample size and adding exploratory substudies.
